This repository contains the computational data supporting the findings of the study titled 'Expanding the paradigm of glycopeptide antibiotic recognition through molecular dynamics simulations'.

The 'Starting Structures' folder contains the DFT optimized structures used as starting models for the study.

The 'Molecular Dynamics Simulations' folder contains the input and output files for GROMACS v2019.3 molecular dynamics simulations. Each system was run in triplicate. Sub-folder indicate whether the glycopeptide antibiotic was complexed with the 'Tripeptide' or 'Polysaccharide II'. 

Glycopeptide antibiotics are abbreviated using the same notation as in the manuscript.

1 - Vancomycin
d1 - Desleucyl Vancomycin
2 - Keratinimicin A
3 - Keratinicylcin B